/src/org.scala-lang/scala-library/2.11.8/src/test/scala/org_scala_lang/scala_library/TrieMapTest.scala`\n- The test serializes and deserializes a populated `TrieMap[String, String]`, exercising:\n  - `TrieMap.writeObject`\n  - `TrieMap.readObject`\n  - key/value serialization loop\n  - serialization end marker handling\n- Removed the scaffold placeholder test:\n  - `Scala_libraryTest.scala`\n\nI did not run compilation or tests, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0deada2f5b146a450169f8facab5848195ae3eab61fba4cbe1\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 788, "output": 889, "cacheRead": 28160, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 29837, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777924797759, "responseId": "resp_0deada2f5b146a450169f8fabe7b3c8195bb8636b7898b9aba"}}
